event.title: Fluid Mechanics Assignment Help
event.description:
Since liquid and gases are both fluids in engineering terms, this unit brings a variety of challenges to students because it deals with continuum analysis of fluids. With the application in aerodynamics, fluid flow in pipes and various close circuit movements of fluids, it is unit with a vast amount of calculation, understanding, and implementation of various laws. With the advancement of technology computational analysis is also added in this unit in modern days. We at My Assignment Help provide online assignment help for all Engineering topics. Our Mechanical Engineering Assignment Help services are capable to cover almost all the topics out of which some are given below:

  1. Volume analysis through Navier-Stokes equation.
  2. Flow similitude, vorticity, circulation, stream function, and velocity potential
  3. Boundary layers and its use in drag and lift evaluation
  4. Fluid turbulence
  5. Compressible flows and its applications
  6. Fluid acoustics
  7. Computational fluid dynamics
  8. Environmental fluid mechanics
  9. Wind energy
